data.description: Completly remodeled and updated...this 4 bedroom/3.5 bath home sits on just over 2.3 acres. This wide open floor plan makes for an ideal entertaining spot, has large rooms, a nice sized bonus/sunroom and a large shop. This property sits in a rural setting and with this much square footage, acreage and a shop, it won't last long! The brick fireplace, high ceilings, beautiful custom stained cabinetry and awesome layout make this one a MUST SEE to appreciate. Call today to schedule your appointment.
